'''史蒂芬·奧格'''（{{lang-en|'''Steven Ogg'''}}）{{BD|1973年|11月4日|catIdx=S史蒂芬·奧格}}，[[加拿大|加拿大]][[演员|演员]]。他曾在《[[法網遊龍|法網遊龍]]》、《[[絕命律師|絕命律師]]》、《[[陰屍路|陰屍路]]》、《[[疑犯追蹤|疑犯追蹤]]》、《[[西方極樂園|西方極樂園]]》以及《[[雪国列车_(电视剧)|末日列車 (影集)]]》中參與演出，亦在2013年出版電玩遊戲《[[俠盜獵車手5|俠盜獵車手5]]》中饰演[[崔佛·菲利普|崔佛·菲利普]]。

==早年生活及初期職業生涯==
史蒂芬生於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[亞伯達|亞伯達]]省的[[卡加利|卡加利]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/gaming/2013/10/09/grand-theft-auto-v-actors/2938165/|title=Interview: Crime pays for 'Grand Theft Auto V' actors|accessdate=2016-10-17|archive-date=2017-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102190424/http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/gaming/2013/10/09/grand-theft-auto-v-actors/2938165/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，從[[加拿大國家電影局|加拿大國家電影局]]開始了他的職業生涯。他原本想往體育領域發展，但後來因為身體受傷使其不得不放棄該方面的追求。

自從他搬到[[紐約市|紐約市]]之後，他便開始在一些電視節目中如《[[絕命律師|絕命律師]]》、《{{link-en|危急最前線|Third Watch}}》中參與演出，除此之外，他並參與了許多電影相關工作及配音演出。在一次修建房屋的個人假期後<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/gaming/2013/10/09/grand-theft-auto-v-actors/2938165/ |title=Interview: Crime pays for 'Grand Theft Auto V' actors |last=Molina |first=Brett |publisher=''[[USA_Today|USA Today]]'' |date=October 9, 2013 |accessdate=November 2, 2013 |archive-date=2017-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170102190424/http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/gaming/2013/10/09/grand-theft-auto-v-actors/2938165/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他被[[Rockstar_Games|Rockstar Games]]聘用為他們2013年電玩遊戲《[[俠盜獵車手5|俠盜獵車手5]]》中[[崔佛·菲利普|崔佛·菲利普]]的配音演員。他所扮演的角色受到極高評價及重視，並成為數個獎項的提名及獲獎人。<ref name="Edge Review">{{cite web |url=http://www.edge-online.com/review/grand-theft-auto-v-review/ |title=Grand Theft Auto V review |author=Edge Staff |date=September 16, 2013 |publisher=[[Edge_(magazine)|Edge]] |accessdate=September 16, 2013 |archive-date=2013-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130919065641/http://www.edge-online.com/review/grand-theft-auto-v-review/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Gamespot Review">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/grand-theft-auto-v-review/1900-6414475/ |title=Grand Theft Auto V Review: City of Angels and Demons |last=Petit |first=Carolyn |date=September 16, 2013 |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=September 16, 2013 |archive-date=2013-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012060924/http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/grand-theft-auto-v-review/1900-6414475/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/blogs/greggy-ign/2013/09/30/new-york-comic-con-2013-lets-hang-out/ |title=New York Comic-Con 2013: Let's Hang Out |last=Miller |first=Greg |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |date=September 30, 2013 |accessdate=November 2, 2013 |archive-date=2017-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170712175821/http://www.ign.com/blogs/greggy-ign/2013/09/30/new-york-comic-con-2013-lets-hang-out |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ign.com/videos/2013/10/11/60-seconds-with-steven-ogg |title=60 Seconds With Steven Ogg |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |date=October 11, 2013 |accessdate=November 2, 2013 |archive-date=2020-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200204110113/https://www.ign.com/videos/2013/10/11/60-seconds-with-steven-ogg |dead-url=no }}</ref> 他在之後並重新回到了[[Youtube|Youtube]]一個小短片「GTA VR」的演出工作中。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-10-11-trevors-back-for-gta-vr|title=Trevor's back for GTA VR film|last=Phillips|first=Tom|date=11 October 2016|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|accessdate=13 October 2016|archive-date=2020-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200204110115/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-10-11-trevors-back-for-gta-vr|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.geek.com/games/gtav-short-film-stars-the-real-trevor-1674442/|title=GTAV Short Film Stars the Real Trevor|last=Polanco|first=Tony|date=11 October 2016|work=Geek.com|accessdate=13 October 2016|archive-date=2020-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200204110122/https://www.geek.com/games/gtav-short-film-stars-the-real-trevor-1674442/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

在《[[陰屍路|陰屍路]]》電視影集第六季最終話中，他扮演的賽門（Simon）成為他在該影集的首亮相，這個角色並會在第七季成為一個固定角色。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.yahoo.com/tech/brand-walking-dead-trailer-probably-revealed-negan-victim-153916930.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-10-17 |archive-date=2016-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011162528/https://www.yahoo.com/tech/brand-walking-dead-trailer-probably-revealed-negan-victim-153916930.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 史蒂芬並在[[HBO|HBO]]電視連續劇《[[西方極樂園|西方極樂園]]》中飾演Rebus。

